title: Coach CEO: Tariffs no Longer in Play Internationally
description: Todd Kahn, CEO and brand president of Coach, discusses the brand’s growth, attributing much of its recent success to a strategic focus on Gen Z consumers. He speaks with Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on “The Close.” (Source: Bloomberg)
